rally linked directly to synuclein-specific pathobiology.\nOverall, this proof-of-concept study shows the potential utility of hitherto\nuncharacterized cross-species structural homologs, identified using comparative\nproteome-wide structure prediction algorithms, in shedding light on abstruse\nconnections among disease-relevant proteins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2015 00:12:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 May 2015 04:33:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-26"}
