etic field enhancement by drift cannot\nsuppress r-mode instability. Results can be generalized for any oscillation\nmode in any medium, if this mode has non-drifting solution for $B=0$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2015 06:36:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-12"}
