ependent and very close to the value\npredicted by Hill, his expression being strictly valid in the rigid filament\nlimit. The average filament force results from the product of the cumulative\nsize fraction x, where the filament is in contact with the wall, times the\nbuckling force on a filament of size L_c ~ L. We discuss several consequences\nof the L independence of the stalling force for our specific filament model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2015 10:32:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2015 10:14:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
